OL,3,CAround two pubs in Britain closing
OL,4,Ceach day, figures show
OL,6,FAround two pubs closed each day in the
OL,7,Ffirst three months of the year amid
OL,8,Fpressure from higher taxes and
OL,9,Fregulatory costs, industry figures
OL,10,Fshow.
OL,12,FThe British Beer and Pub Association
OL,13,F(BBPA) warned that 161 pubs closed
OL,14,Facross Britain in the first quarter of
OL,15,Fthe year.
OL,17,FThis equates to the loss of around
OL,18,F2,400 jobs, with a particular hit to
OL,19,Fyounger workers.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
