OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1777971986
OL,3,CAround two pubs in Britain closing
OL,4,Ceach day, figures show
OL,6,FIt represents a 26% jump in closures
OL,7,Fcompared to the same period last year,
OL,8,Fwith local pubs having come under
OL,9,Fpressure from rising labour costs,
OL,10,Ftaxes and caution among consumers.
OL,12,FEarly this year, the government
OL,13,Fannounced business rates support for
OL,14,Fpubs after warnings from the sector
OL,15,Fthat further tax changes could lead to
OL,16,Fmore closures and job losses.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
