OL,3,CAround two pubs in Britain closing
OL,4,Ceach day, figures show
OL,6,FA 15% tax relief for pubs and music
OL,7,Fvenues came into effect last month `
OL,8,Fbut measures from last November's
OL,9,Fbudget, such as an increase in the
OL,10,Fminimum wage, still added to a
OL,11,Fsignificant jump in business costs for
OL,12,Fpubs and brewers.
OL,14,FThe BBPA said the latest closure
OL,15,Ffigures highlight a need for longer-
OL,16,Fterm changes to business rates and a
OL,17,Fwider overhaul of taxes on the
OL,18,Fhospitality sector.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
