OL,3,CAround two pubs in Britain closing
OL,4,Ceach day, figures show
OL,6,FIts chief executive, Emma McClarkin,
OL,7,Fsaid: "The scale of these closures is
OL,8,Favoidable because pubs are doing a
OL,9,Fbrisk trade, but their profits are
OL,10,Fwiped out by a disproportionate tax
OL,11,Fburden and huge costs.
OL,13,F"For too many, the sheer weight of
OL,14,Ftaxes and regulatory costs have forced
OL,15,Fthem to shut up shop, which will only
OL,16,Fhurt communities, workers, and the
OL,17,Fwider economy.
OL,26,@oD@GOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
