OL,3,CAround two pubs in Britain closing
OL,4,Ceach day, figures show
OL,6,F"This underscores why government's
OL,7,Fbusiness rates relief was so
OL,8,Fnecessary, and the support such a
OL,9,Fwelcome relief.
OL,11,F"We want to work with government to
OL,12,Festablish a permanent long-term plan
OL,13,Fthat will deliver permanently lower
OL,14,Fbills, a fairer system and ultimately
OL,15,Fprotect this treasured sector."
OL,17,FHere are the number of closures in
OL,18,Feach British region:
