OL,3,CAround two pubs in Britain closing
OL,4,Ceach day, figures show
OL,6,FLast year Britain lost 336 pubs,
OL,7,Fbringing the total down to 44,656,
OL,8,Findustry figures showed. This meant
OL,9,Fthat more than 2,000 pubs had closed
OL,10,Fsince the outbreak of the coronavirus
OL,11,Fpandemic in 2020.
OL,13,FWales was the only part of Great
OL,14,FBritain to report a rise in pub
OL,15,Fnumbers in the latest data, while
OL,16,FScotland witnessed the heaviest fall
OL,17,Fin numbers.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
