OL,3,CAround two pubs in Britain closing
OL,4,Ceach day, figures show
OL,6,FThe UK Spirits Alliance, which
OL,7,Frepresents hundreds of distillers
OL,8,Facross Britain, urged the government
OL,9,Fto carry out a "proper review" of
OL,10,Fexcise duty as hospitality is
OL,11,F"fighting for our very survival".
OL,13,FNeema Rai, spokeswoman for the group
OL,14,Fand co-founder of Westminster-based
OL,15,FTamesis Dock and the Battersea Barge,
OL,16,Fsaid: "Pubs have been hit hard in
OL,17,Frecent years and we've just been hit
OL,18,Fby yet another excise duty hike.
OL,26,@qD@POUqD@^O]sD@AOUsD@`O]xD@GOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
