OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1777971986
OL,3,CAround two pubs in Britain closing
OL,4,Ceach day, figures show
OL,6,F"Spirits offer higher profit margins
OL,7,Fand help keep us afloat, yet we have
OL,8,Fthe highest rate of excise duty in the
OL,9,FG7.
OL,11,F"The government needs to carry out a
OL,12,Fproper review of excise duty if it's
OL,13,Fserious about supporting hospitality
OL,14,Fbecause we're fighting for our very
OL,15,Fsurvival."
