OL,3,CAround two pubs in Britain closing
OL,4,Ceach day, figures show
OL,6,FA government spokesperson said: "We
OL,7,Fare backing Britain's pubs ` cutting
OL,8,FApril's business rates bills by 15%
OL,9,Ffollowed by a two-year freeze,
OL,10,Fextending World Cup opening hours and
OL,11,Fincreasing the Hospitality Support
OL,12,FFund to #10 million to help venues
OL,13,Fgrow.
OL,15,F"Later this year, we'll also build on
OL,16,Four Pride in Place programme with our
OL,17,Fnew High Streets Strategy to
OL,18,Frevitalise our town centres.
OL,26,@nD@aOUwD@AOU
