OL,3,CAround two pubs in Britain closing
OL,4,Ceach day, figures show
OL,6,F"This comes on top of capping
OL,7,Fcorporation tax, cutting alcohol duty
OL,8,Fon draught pints and six cuts in
OL,9,Finterest rates, benefiting businesses
OL,10,Fin every part of Britain."
